\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The impossibly huge dormant volcano towers over the nearby mountains. It's black outline looms like a headless monster standing waist deep in a pile of jagged rocks. The starless sky soon gives way to the first golden rays of sunlight. The mechanical Sun awakens, transforming the landscape into a jungle covered mountain range, sparkling in the noon day light. A floating glimmer of metal reflects the sunlight, disrupting the perfect blue sky.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 A loud deep alarm sound shatters the peace. Massive turrets half buried in the overgrown hillside spring to life, shaking birds and bushes as they turn to aim at the aircraft. }
