\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'll catch up with you guys in a minute!}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Callie is led to the left down a hallway, while the Male Greeter takes Mike, Richard and Aaron through a doorway on the far wall. The other Female Greeter shuts the door behind them. }
