\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The tunnels are just lit enough to make the damp walls shine. None of them bother to use the rusty hand rails as they make their way deeper into the rock.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 They follow the Male Greeter down cement stairs through the the lava rock to a large metal door. The Greeter opens the door for them and steps aside to let them pass.}
