\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The doorway leads to a metal catwalk extending a few hundred feet past rows of iron cell doors. There is open area in the middle, revealing a second level of cells below them. Beyond the open area is an identical row of cells, like the ones in front of them. Most of the cages are empty, but a few have prisoners sitting on benches, reading or eating. Two skylights at either end of the room provide most of the light. }
