\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I do hope you don't try anything stupid. That gun is completely automated, and will prevent any violence.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mike turns slowly to see the turret aiming at him and carefully places his weapon on the floor.}
